OL,3,CSpike in deaths and patients in
OL,4,Chospital: How prevalent is Covid?
OL,6,FAt the beginning of the pandemic,
OL,7,Ffamilies across the country were glued
OL,8,Fto their television screens, waiting
OL,9,Fto be told the latest data on the
OL,10,Fsituation.
OL,12,FFour years on, the Covid Inquiry has
OL,13,Fpublished it's first damning report
OL,14,Finto the failures from the UK
OL,15,Fgovernment and civil service in
OL,16,Fpreparing for the virus.
