OL,3,CSpike in deaths and patients in
OL,4,Chospital: How prevalent is Covid?
OL,6,FIt said there was a "damaging absence
OL,7,Fof focus" on the measures and
OL,8,Finfrastructure that would be needed to
OL,9,Fdeal with a fast-spreading disease,
OL,10,Feven though a coronavirus outbreak at
OL,11,Fpandemic scale "was foreseeable".
OL,13,FBut as the inquiry looks back, ITV
OL,14,FNews compares the data closest to July
OL,15,F18 across the past few years, to
OL,16,Fbetter determine the prevalence of
OL,17,FCovid today.
