OL,3,CSpike in deaths and patients in
OL,4,Chospital: How prevalent is Covid?
OL,6,FAn aggregate estimate of 25 million
OL,7,FCovid cases have been recorded in the
OL,8,FUK, but the real figure is thought to
OL,9,Fmuch higher.
OL,11,FPositive tests are significantly lower
OL,12,Fthan they have been at various peaks
OL,13,Fsince the pandemic began.
OL,15,FBut the data is limited since most
OL,16,Fpeople were advised to no longer take
OL,17,Fa Covid test if they suspected they
OL,18,Fwere infected since the vaccine was
OL,19,Frolled out.
