OL,3,CSpike in deaths and patients in
OL,4,Chospital: How prevalent is Covid?
OL,6,FWhen testing was in full swing in
OL,7,F2021, cases were recorded at 38, 475
OL,8,Fon July 18.
OL,10,FBy the same day in 2023 this had
OL,11,Ffallen to 517 and by July 10, 2024 -
OL,12,Fthe latest available UK Health
OL,13,FSecurity Agency (UKHSA) data it had
OL,14,Fdropped to 142.
OL,16,FPatients in hospital with Covid
OL,18,FFewer than 5,000 people have been
OL,19,Fhospitalised by Covid since the
OL,20,Fbeginning of 2023, after the number
OL,21,Fpeaked at 25,000 in January 2021.
