OL,3,CSpike in deaths and patients in
OL,4,Chospital: How prevalent is Covid?
OL,6,FIn a similar downwards trend, the
OL,7,Fdaily number of beds occupied by Covid
OL,8,Fpatients has fallen.
OL,10,FOn July 31 in 2020, 2021 and 2020
OL,11,Fthere were over 100,000 beds being
OL,12,Fused to treat people with the virus.
OL,13,FBy May 31, 2023 this had fallen to
OL,14,Fjust 77 beds.
OL,16,FBut this year that number has risen
OL,17,Fagain with 1, 886 hospital beds taken
OL,18,Fup by Covid patients on the same day
OL,19,Fin 2024.
