OL,3,CSpike in deaths and patients in
OL,4,Chospital: How prevalent is Covid?
OL,6,FIn a broader trend, Covid-related
OL,7,Fdeaths almost halved from 32,300 in
OL,8,F2022 to 16,600 in 2023.
OL,10,FBut according to the latest UKHSA
OL,11,Fdetailing the number of weekly Covid
OL,12,Fdeaths cited on death certificates,
OL,13,Fthere were 168 deaths in the seven
OL,14,Fdays prior to June 28, 2024.
OL,16,FThat is up from 55 deaths a year
OL,17,Fearlier, but is still lower than 2022
OL,18,Fwhen deaths were close to 700 in a
OL,19,Fsimilar period.
