OL,3,CSpike in deaths and patients in
OL,4,Chospital: How prevalent is Covid?
OL,6,FThere are no longer Covid restrictions
OL,7,Fin place, but it is advised you stay
OL,8,Fat home if possible should you test
OL,9,Fpositive.
OL,11,FDr Alexander Allen, Consultant
OL,12,FEpidemiologist at UKHSA, told ITV News
OL,13,Fthat the body continues to monitor the
OL,14,Fsituation closely and trends in recent
OL,15,Fweeks have seen a spike in Covid.
