OL,3,CSpike in deaths and patients in
OL,4,Chospital: How prevalent is Covid?
OL,6,F"We know most summer activities are
OL,7,Fspent with others, but taking some
OL,8,Ftime out to get better when you're
OL,9,Funwell also helps prevent the spread
OL,10,Fof viruses and protects others,
OL,11,Fespecially those who are more
OL,12,Fvulnerable," he said.
OL,14,F"If you have symptoms of a respiratory
OL,15,Fvirus, like a new continuous cough or
OL,16,Ffever, we continue to advise avoiding
OL,17,Fcontact with others.
