OL,6,F"If you do need to leave home,
OL,7,Fconsider wearing a mask in crowded
OL,8,Fplaces. Simple actions like catching
OL,9,Fcoughs and sneezes with a tissue,
OL,10,Fwashing your hands regularly, and
OL,11,Fimproving indoor ventilation can help
OL,12,Fto reduce the spread of viruses."
OL,14,FThe Office for National statistics
OL,15,Fmonitored the majority of Covid data
OL,16,Fthrough the Coronavirus Infection
OL,17,FSurvey until March 2023. It was
OL,18,Fsucceeded by the UKHSA.
